(June 27, 1962)

In decisions Nos. 1-13 : Present—Coon, J. P., Gibson, Herlihy, Reynolds and Taylor, JJ.

In the Matter of the Claim of Richard A. McMaster, Respondent, v. Jamestown Veneer & Plywood Corporation et al., Appellants. Workmen’s Compensation Board, Respondent.

Motion to accept late filing of respondent Workmen’s Compensation Board’s brief denied, without costs.
